OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774185071
OL,3,CIllegal waste site shut down by
OL,4,CEnvironment Agency in Kent
OL,6,FAn illegal waste site in Ramsgate in
OL,7,FKent has been shut down by the
OL,8,FEnvironment Agency.
OL,10,FOfficers were called to Haine
OL,11,FIndustrial Estate in Newington to
OL,12,Freports of bags of shredded waste from
OL,13,Fa member of the public.
OL,15,FAfter visiting the site on 4 March,
OL,16,Fconcrete blocks have been placed
OL,17,Foutside the gates at the entrance of
OL,18,FUnits 26 and 27 at Leigh Road.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
