OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774185071
OL,3,CIllegal waste site shut down by
OL,4,CEnvironment Agency in Kent
OL,6,FThis means anyone entering the land
OL,7,Fwithout reasonable excuse or written
OL,8,Fpermission from the Environment Agency
OL,9,Fwill be committing a criminal offence,
OL,10,Fas will anyone who tampers with the
OL,11,Flock or notice.
OL,13,FMatt Higginson, Environment Manager at
OL,14,Fthe Environment Agency said: "This
OL,15,Forder follows on from the successful
OL,16,FRestriction Orders we obtained at
OL,17,FEastchurch and Minister on the Isle of
OL,18,FSheppey and at Hoads Wood near
OL,19,FAshford, and shows we will act against
OL,20,Fthose who flout the law.
OL,26,@vD@^OU
