PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774185071
OL,3,CIllegal waste site shut down by
OL,4,CEnvironment Agency in Kent
OL,6,F"We know illegal waste activity harms
OL,7,Fthe environment and has a devastating
OL,8,Feffect on communities.
OL,10,F"Our priority is protecting the local
OL,11,Fcommunity and environment.
OL,13,F"This order has been secured following
OL,14,Fthe local community's concerns and the
OL,15,Fenvironmental impact of the tipping of
OL,16,Fwaste at the site.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
