OL,3,CIllegal waste site shut down by
OL,4,CEnvironment Agency in Kent
OL,6,F"If people see or suspect illegal
OL,7,Ftipping of waste, they can report it
OL,8,Fto us on our 24/7 Incident Hotline on
OL,9,F0800 80 70 60 or report it anonymously
OL,10,Fto Crimestoppers 0800 555111".
